citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1415 on
29-Aug-17.
Inspector arrival to facility at 1415. Closed sign on door of shop with additional sign stating shop was closing at
1:30 pm on Tuesday. Called telephone # and left message. Inspector departure at 1445.
